<h1> Raspberry pi (version 3)</h1>
<h3>What is Raspberry pi?</h3>
<p>Raspberry pi is a single board with a wireless LAN and Bluetooth connectivity. This is a credit card sized electronic board, like the one you would find inside your computer or laptop just smaller.</p>

<h3>What would you purchase raspberry pi?</h3>
<p>Why would you purchase <strong>raspberry pi?</strong> Its only $35 which is the price for 64-bit quad-core ARM cortex-A53 CPU intergreated  802.11 wireless LAN and bluetooth.</p>
    
<h3>What use do they have?</h3>
<p>with raspberry pi you can make it a little web browser by connecting it to your tv. You can also make robots with the board.</p>


